301
00:32:55,737 --> 00:32:57,114
And they were documents

302
00:32:57,661 --> 00:32:59,163
operations briefs

303
00:32:59,634 --> 00:33:01,428
unusual phones and.

304
00:33:02,616 --> 00:33:04,022
I saw a gun.

305
00:33:05,733 --> 00:33:07,419
I thought you were just
scaring us when you said.

306
00:33:07,443 --> 00:33:09,612
Ate Allison is a secret agent.

307
00:33:12,869 --> 00:33:14,469
It turns out you were telling the truth.

308
00:33:19,304 --> 00:33:20,973
I heard her one night

309
00:33:20,998 --> 00:33:22,916
talking to someone over the phone,

310
00:33:24,638 --> 00:33:26,866
