313
00:33:34,634 --> 00:33:37,296
I got curious, Zein.

314
00:33:39,541 --> 00:33:40,876
I don't know what got into me

315
00:33:41,200 --> 00:33:42,534
when I stole the map

316
00:33:42,561 --> 00:33:43,771
from her room.

317
00:33:46,191 --> 00:33:48,318
I couldn't even understand her notes.

318
00:33:48,890 --> 00:33:50,030
What I know is

319
00:33:51,796 --> 00:33:52,928
she was trying to find.

320
00:33:52,953 --> 00:33:54,789
Hell University.

321
00:33:55,866 --> 00:33:57,409
I'm sorry, Zein.

322
00:34:01,747 --> 00:34:04,375
A lot things happened to us
because Mia brought us here.

323
00:34:06,124 --> 00:34:08,543
Our lives have been in constant danger.

324
00:34:15,629 --> 00:34:16,772
Lift it up!

325
00:34:17,277 --> 00:34:18,403
