341
00:35:35,424 --> 00:35:36,425
Matt!

342
00:35:39,595 --> 00:35:40,446
Bro!

343
00:35:40,471 --> 00:35:41,354
Bro!

344
00:35:41,472 --> 00:35:42,556
Wake him up!

345
00:35:43,063 --> 00:35:45,775
Bro, wake up!

346
00:35:55,277 --> 00:35:57,654
Zein, what happened to the two of you?

347
00:36:05,704 --> 00:36:06,704
Where's Zein?

348
00:36:06,955 --> 00:36:08,916
