382
00:37:49,216 --> 00:37:51,310
It's my fault we're here.

383
00:37:52,394 --> 00:37:54,716
I hope you told us
about this from the start.

384
00:37:58,525 --> 00:38:00,611
We can't do anything about it anymore.

385
00:38:01,737 --> 00:38:03,196
This is our reality now.

386
00:38:09,152 --> 00:38:11,510
This won't end like this.

387
00:38:13,540 --> 00:38:15,375
