388
00:38:41,640 --> 00:38:42,640
Take her.

389
00:38:43,172 --> 00:38:44,173
No!

390
00:38:44,488 --> 00:38:45,634
No, don't take her!

391
00:38:46,865 --> 00:38:47,865
No!

392
00:38:47,890 --> 00:38:49,516
Stop!

393
00:38:50,744 --> 00:38:51,870
Let her go!

394
00:38:52,204 --> 00:38:53,204
Zein!

395
00:38:54,665 --> 00:38:55,665
Take her too.

396
00:38:57,376 --> 00:38:58,376
Mia!

397
00:38:59,503 --> 00:39:00,503
Zein!

398
00:39:12,099 --> 00:39:13,099
Zein!

399
00:39:16,365 --> 00:39:17,365
Mia!

400
00:39:23,604 --> 00:39:24,604
Zein!

401
00:39:25,070 --> 00:39:26,070
Zein!

402
00:39:26,780 --> 00:39:27,780
Zein!

403
00:39:29,790 --> 00:39:30,790
Zein!

404
00:39:36,498 --> 00:39:37,498
Zein!

405
00:39:40,585 --> 00:39:41,585
Stop!

406
00:39:49,842 --> 00:39:50,842
Zein!

407
00:39:53,282 --> 00:39:54,282
Zein!

408
00:39:54,307 --> 00:39:55,307
Zein!

409
00:39:56,226 --> 00:39:57,519
Run, Mia!

410
00:40:06,153 --> 00:40:07,612
Let me go!

411
00:40:08,055 --> 00:40:09,390
I said let me go!

412
00:40:31,077 --> 00:40:32,870
- Hurry up!
- I'm on it!

413
00:40:33,337 --> 00:40:34,337
Hurry!

414
00:40:34,431 --> 00:40:35,431
Mia!

415
00:40:35,974 --> 00:40:37,034
- Mia, over here!
- Dave!

416
00:40:37,059 --> 00:40:38,060
Mia!

417
00:40:38,560 --> 00:40:39,895
- Mia!
- Faster!

418
00:40:39,920 --> 00:40:41,378
Please, hurry!

419
00:40:42,689 --> 00:40:44,357
Mia, I'm glad you're safe.

420
00:40:45,150 --> 00:40:46,384
Where are the others?

421
00:40:46,985 --> 00:40:48,653
- Where's Zein and Matt?
- Where are they?

422
00:40:48,695 --> 00:40:49,738
Zein will follow us out.

423
00:40:49,763 --> 00:40:50,763
