424
00:40:50,947 --> 00:40:51,590
Fuck!

425
00:40:51,615 --> 00:40:53,008
Shit, let's go!

426
00:40:53,033 --> 00:40:54,076
Let's go! Hurry!

427
00:41:05,420 --> 00:41:06,420
