453
00:42:31,412 --> 00:42:34,665
We've known for a while that there's
a traitor among the Black Blood Gang.

454
00:42:35,135 --> 00:42:37,387
Someone leaking info to the admin.

455
00:42:37,971 --> 00:42:40,098
That's why we were
blinded by the gas attack

456
00:42:41,116 --> 00:42:42,659
because our eyes on the operation

457
00:42:42,684 --> 00:42:44,603
is the traitor.

458
00:42:45,328 --> 00:42:46,762
We need to find him.

459
00:42:47,527 --> 00:42:49,925
He's the one who knows
where they kept the students.

460
00:42:49,983 --> 00:42:51,651
And your friends.

461
00:42:52,152 --> 00:42:53,361
Zein was taken too.

462
00:42:54,106 --> 00:42:55,399
I need to find her.

463
00:42:56,531 --> 00:42:57,531
Wow

464
00:42:58,060 --> 00:42:59,937
you really love her, don't you?

465
00:43:01,571 --> 00:43:02,747
I loved her

466
00:43:03,038 --> 00:43:04,038
ever since.

467
00:43:05,332 --> 00:43:08,460
And you'll sacrifice your life for her?

468
00:43:09,252 --> 00:43:10,252
Yes

469
00:43:12,067 --> 00:43:14,736
cause she will do the
same for me and her friends.

470
00:43:15,400 --> 00:43:17,569
She values her friends' lives

471
00:43:17,695 --> 00:43:19,114
more than her own life.

472
00:43:21,858 --> 00:43:23,151
She may be hot headed

473
00:43:23,521 --> 00:43:25,231
and quick to fight

474
00:43:25,903 --> 00:43:26,903
but

475
00:43:28,127 --> 00:43:29,127
