478
00:43:36,196 --> 00:43:38,531
I wasn't wrong in choosing you.

479
00:43:39,074 --> 00:43:40,951
But don't act on your own.

480
00:43:41,895 --> 00:43:44,731
Especially while we don't know
where they kept the others yet.

481
00:43:45,914 --> 00:43:47,165
We need to regroup.

482
00:43:48,541 --> 00:43:49,918
We should take care of Luke first.

483
00:43:51,544 --> 00:43:52,312
Fine.

484
00:43:52,337 --> 00:43:53,337
Okay?

485
00:43:53,804 --> 00:43:54,778
Let's go.

486
00:44:18,280 --> 00:44:19,544
Hello, secretary.

487
00:44:19,929 --> 00:44:21,305
How are you?

488
00:44:22,492 --> 00:44:24,202
I'm better than fine.

489
00:44:25,662 --> 00:44:27,747
Well this is our hidden laboratory.

490
00:44:29,219 --> 00:44:31,137
Supremo will come for me.

491
00:44:32,473 --> 00:44:34,073
You don't know him like I do.

492
00:44:34,597 --> 00:44:35,765
He's coming.

493
00:45:04,317 --> 00:45:06,879
Haven't you all felt angry?

494
00:45:08,747 --> 00:45:11,374
Angry from their injustice?

495
00:45:11,499 --> 00:45:12,583
Nobody move!

496
00:45:12,584 --> 00:45:13,584
Guys, get down.

497
00:45:20,633 --> 00:45:21,801
What are the chances?

498
00:45:22,028 --> 00:45:25,614
Aside from the special treatment
that Supremo has been giving you

499
00:45:25,639 --> 00:45:27,439
there's actually something
special about you.

500
00:45:28,451 --> 00:45:30,577
An exceptionally rare blood type

501
00:45:30,602 --> 00:45:33,396
with an exceptionally rare blood component.

502
00:45:33,733 --> 00:45:35,694
They're preparing her for the extraction.

503
00:45:36,941 --> 00:45:38,985
Violet's going to get what she wants.

504
00:45:39,277 --> 00:45:41,404
This hell will finally end.

505
00:45:43,698 --> 00:45:46,951
I am Supremo.

506
00:45:47,660 --> 00:45:49,412
I will not fail.

507
00:45:55,168 --> 00:45:56,168
Seal the door!

508
00:45:59,294 --> 00:46:00,676
Ou don't know him like I do.

509
00:46:01,674 --> 00:46:02,884
He's coming for me.
